window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Survival is no longer a choice. It's a game.</b></p> <p>When the Doom System appeared, it shattered reality overnight. People took superhuman abilities, their only defense against a world that no longer made sense. But just as humanity began to adapt, the System changed the rules.</p> <p>Now, survival isn’t just a struggle. It’s a competition.</p> <p>For Hiro Johnson, staying alive has become a full-time job. The System twists the streets of New York into death traps, pitting survivors against monsters, hunters, and each other yet rewarding them with powerful skills and weapons.</p> <p>But something is wrong. The System is failing. It glitches, hallucinates, makes up rules as it goes...</p> <p>This isn’t just a death game. It’s a system breaking in real time.</p> <p>And if Hiro can’t find a way to fight back, there won’t be anything left to save.</p> <p><b>Don't miss the start of a new action-packed Apocalyptic LitRPG by bestselling author Harmon Cooper. It's perfect for fans of </b><b><i>Primal Hunter</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>System Apocalypse</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Defiance of the Fall</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
